title: Casey White indicated he wanted a shootout, but wreck prevented it, sheriff says - CNN
content: Casey White indicated he wanted a shootout, but wreck prevented it, sheriff says  CNNView Full Coverage on Google News
description: Authorities are releasing new details of the final moments of Monday's police chase that ended fugitive inmate Casey White's 11 days on the run with a former corrections officer -- who authorities say may have ended her own life during the pursuit.
